{"tid":1897730,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"開心！夏蘭特收到偶像米祖的簽名波衫","createTime":"2020-02-26T01:42:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T02:26:54.000Z","uid":73381,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"629bee979b13acdd630c2254a2fcc12bac0b739d","tid":1897730,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T01:42:58.000Z","msg":"新加盟多蒙特的夏蘭特，在今季迅速成為球壇最閃耀的一顆新星，在短短6場德甲聯賽中，已極速攻入9個入球，風頭一時無兩。<br />\n<br />\n對不少新一代球員而言，C朗及美斯絕對是他們的偶像；但對英國列斯出生的夏蘭特而言，他卻有與眾不同的品味。<br />\n<br />\n夏蘭特鍾愛曾效力史雲斯的西班牙箭頭米捷（Michu），現年33歲的米捷在2017年高掛球靴，現時在一間西班牙第三級別球會Burgos擔任體育總監。夏蘭特除了心底喜愛米捷外，更在個人Instagram中吸引偶像的注意，不斷在自己的相片中標籤米捷。<br />\n<br />\n當米捷得知夏蘭特是他的忠實球迷後，他送上現時球會的球衣，並印上夏蘭特的名字及17號，米捷亦在球衣上簽上自己簽名。"},{"pid":"5df65cd8b7849fc3bfd1b9deaf2c4f6c0a2f81d2","tid":1897730,"uid":286626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T01:44:20.000Z","msg":"一出道勁過偶像好少見吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54865818c47ff26fcb144894db6ffef8cd9ace46","tid":1897730,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T01:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4055832/org/3bcf483f22ec446ce19839d11edf6162.jpg/AV3zyPIuZ9zQ04HcYuPmiajCFCueslNRD3EzDw9xMw8?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4055832%2Forg%2F3bcf483f22ec446ce19839d11edf6162.jpg%2FAV3zyPIuZ9zQ04HcYuPmiajCFCueslNRD3EzDw9xMw8%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=28a19ba0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夏蘭特經常在自己貼文中標籤米捷。（Instagram截圖）"},{"pid":"c71b94ec7b812b319f2eb313491380215cc6cbd1","tid":1897730,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T01:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4055831/org/4c585d4f9d41bdddd74b4d7797700e35.JPG/121VMYxKLstqdYlO1th-LgWH62ePJb2FJ9JtiyfSbYs?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4055831%2Forg%2F4c585d4f9d41bdddd